Key Match Events: Royce Lewis ended a slump with a two-run double and a near-grand slam that became a double; Brooks Lee also ended his slump with a two-run double
Post-Match Reflections: Twins manager Rocco Baldelli praised Lewis's performance and the bullpen's efforts
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game involved several relievers, and there was a flyover remembrance of 9/11
Others: The Twins won the series, taking two out of three games against the Angels
